data.description: Completely renovated home on a double lot in sought after North Elementary School Dist. This 5 bed/4.5 bath home features an abundance of living space with high end finishes at every turn.  Three bedrooms provide private, attached baths. The white kitchen offers solid surface counters and European gas range.  Low maintenance laminate flooring runs throughout the entire home which also boasts tiled baths and tankless hot water.  Ample exterior entertaining space with 2 decks and a patio including a sunken firepit and basketball court. Upgrades including underground pet fence, hard-wired Tesla charger and hot tub remain.  Located within a mile of WVU/Mon General Hosp and Suncrest Town Center but with the peaceful tranquility of being surrounded by the WVU Farm.
